textBeforeTable: Track listing[edit] 5 References 4 Samples 3 Chart positions 2 Personnel 1 Track listing Contents Death Before Dishonor is the debut album by rapper 2 Pistols, released on June 17, 2008. Guests include T-Pain, Tay Dizm, Ray J, Slick Pulla, Blood Raw, Trey Songz, BMU & Tyra B. A version of "Candy Coated Diamonds" featuring Fergie (instead of Tyra B) leaked on various The Black Eyed Peas fansites. 4/10[3] RapReviews [2] DJ Booth
